    "TransformBy[{a1, a2, ...} -> {b1, b2, ...}, m] returns a list of rules \
ai -> \\[CapitalSigma]j mij bj, which can be used in ReplaceAll, by applying \
the linear transformation associated with matrix m. TransformBy[{a11, a12, \
...} -> {b11, b12, ...}, {a21, a22, ...} -> {b21, b22, ...}, ..., m] returns \
a list of rules aki -> \\[CapitalSigma]j mij bkj (notice the same m for all \
k). TransformBy[expr, {a11, a12, ...} -> {b11, b12, ...}, {a21, a22, ...} -> \
{b21, b22, ...}, ..., m] applies ReplaceAll with the resulting rules on \
expr.", "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "TransformBy", 
